3V3 → VCC/EN-V
GND → GND
GPIO2 → SCLK (AS3935 SCK)
GPIO3 → MOSI
GPIO4 → MISO
GPIO7 → CS
GPIO1 → IRQ (use sensor’s IRQ pin; open-drain → keep pullup)

Tries to connect to saved Wi-Fi. If it can’t in ~15s → starts SoftAP: AS3935-Setup (pass 12345678).
  http://192.168.4.1/ → enter your SSID/PASS
Once on your LAN, the OLED shows IP + port and as3935.local (mDNS).
  Open http://as3935.local/
Press BOOT → OLED switches to a “monitor” screen
